---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="AI Intelligence Integration | Intelio - Intelligent Automation for Business" description="Embed AI-powered analysis, scoring, and automation into your existing workflows. Remove routine analysis. Improve decision quality. Apply intelligence where it creates real leverage.">
<main class="bg-white">
  <!-- ENHANCED HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-black">
    <!-- Video Background -->
    <video 
      autoplay 
      loop 
      muted 
      playsinline
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40"
    >
      <source src="/logos/AI_Network_Animation_Generation.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
            AI Integration
          </span>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight">
          AI Intelligence Integration
        </h1>
        
        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-200 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Intelligent automation and decision support built into your workflows.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          AI is everywhere. Most of it is useless. Real AI creates leverage. We integrate it only where it creates undeniable business value. Applied precisely. Embedded seamlessly. Measured ruthlessly.
        </p>
        
        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="#what-we-build" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
            Explore Intelligence Integration
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white/30 hover:border-white/60 text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300">
            Schedule Discovery
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-10 animate-bounce">
      <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CREDIBILITY BAR -->
  <section class="py-12 px-6 bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">Trusted by operations leaders at:</p>
        <!-- Client Logos - Infinite Scroll -->
        <div class="logo-marquee-container w-full">
          <div class="logo-marquee-track">
            <!-- First set of logos -->
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/Newmark-logo.png" alt="Newmark" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">Newmark</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/hhp-grey-logo.png" alt="HHP" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">HHP</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/alliance-resource.png" alt="Alliance Resource Partners" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Alliance Resource Partners</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/manhattan-construction-logo.png" alt="Manhattan Construction" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Manhattan Construction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/brain-body-soul-logo.png" alt="Brain Body Soul" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Brain Body Soul</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/JLL-Logo.png" alt="JLL" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">JLL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/CB logo.png" alt="CB" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">CB</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Duplicate set for seamless loop -->
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/Newmark-logo.png" alt="Newmark" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">Newmark</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/hhp-grey-logo.png" alt="HHP" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">HHP</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/alliance-resource.png" alt="Alliance Resource Partners" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Alliance Resource Partners</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/manhattan-construction-logo.png" alt="Manhattan Construction" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Manhattan Construction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/brain-body-soul-logo.png" alt="Brain Body Soul" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Brain Body Soul</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/JLL-Logo.png" alt="JLL" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">JLL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/CB logo.png" alt="CB" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">CB</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM SECTION -->
  <section class="problem-section py-20 md:py-24 px-6 bg-white relative">
    <!-- Left Accent Line (Animated) -->
    <div class="problem-accent-line absolute left-0 top-0 w-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full z-10"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="mb-16 scroll-fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-6 inline-block pb-4 border-b-4 border-blue-600">
          The Analysis Burden That's Eating Your Productivity
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed mt-6 mb-12">
          Your team is drowning in routine analysis. Sales reps spend hours qualifying leads. Customer success teams manually score churn risk. Deal teams analyze separately when matching should be automatic. This is data processing disguised as skilled labor.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10 relative pl-8">
        <!-- Problem 1 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-600 mb-3">Manual Analysis Doesn't Scale</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                You can have one analyst review 100 deals per week. You can't scale that to 10,000 deals. You could hire more analysts, but that's throwing headcount at a process problem. Or your team just stops analyzing, which means decisions get worse.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 2 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-600 mb-3">Humans Are Inconsistent</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Person A scores lead quality as 7/10. Person B scores the same lead as 5/10. Your lead database is worthless because it's inconsistent. Routing decisions are random because scoring is random. You're making decisions on garbage data.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 3 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-600 mb-3">Patterns Are Hidden in Complexity</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                There are relationships in your data that no human will spot. Certain buyer profiles close 60% of deals with certain property types. Certain customer segments have 3x churn risk. Certain deal characteristics predict 90-day close probability. These patterns exist in your data right now. Your team just can't see them because humans can't hold 50 variables in their head simultaneously.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 4 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-600 mb-3">Analysis Takes Too Long</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                A customer calls asking "do I have supply chain risk?" Your customer success rep spends 30 minutes pulling data. Could be answered in 5 seconds. That slow response speed compounds across 1,000 customers. Hours of productivity lost.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 5 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-600 mb-3">Good Analysts Are Expensive and Hard to Find</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Hiring someone to do high-level analysis work? Expect to pay six figures. Finding someone good? Expect to wait six months. And the moment they start understanding your business, they're a flight risk. So you just stop analyzing. That's not a strategy. That's surrender.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE BUILD SECTION -->
  <section id="what-we-build" class="py-20 md:py-24 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Intelligence That Actually Works
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-600 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          AI is only valuable when it removes manual work or improves decisions. We integrate intelligence precisely where it creates that leverage. Not everywhere. Not for show. Exactly where it matters.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Card 1: Database Architecture -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 0ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">01</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-blue-600 mb-3">Unstructured Data Becomes Usable Information</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Contracts, emails, PDFs—most data is unstructured. AI extracts key information, identifies risks, flags anomalies. What took 30 minutes takes 30 seconds.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Intelligent Automation -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 100ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">02</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-blue-600 mb-3">The Right Work Reaches the Right Person at the Right Time</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            AI learns what matters. Ready leads route to sales. At-risk customers flag to success. Consistent evaluation. Fast decisions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Custom Interfaces -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">03</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17V7m0 10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10V7m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2a2 2 0 00-2 2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-blue-600 mb-3">Every Record Gets Smarter</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Your CRM knows a name. AI enriches it with growth signals, intent, market data. Smarter data. Better decisions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4: Seamless Integration -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 300ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">04</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-blue-600 mb-3">Instant Answers to Common Questions</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Same questions every week. AI answers instantly. 24/7. Always consistent. Your team gets answers without pestering departments.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 5: Infrastructure -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 400ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">05</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4 4 0 003 15z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-blue-600 mb-3">See the Future. Plan Accordingly.</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            AI forecasting analyzes dozens of variables. Pipeline, patterns, performance, signals. More accurate forecasts. Better decisions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 6: Intelligence -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 500ms;">
